Significance: minor
Type: enhancement

Track transactional email outcomes: log when emails are disabled (is_enabled() false) or skipped (no recipient, already sent) in addition to the existing send-attempt logging.

Also fixes a locale leak in WC_Email_New_Order::trigger() where restore_locale() was not called on the already-sent early-return path, and adds a defensive instanceof guard before updating order meta on a successful send.
